{#- TL;DR · how NY pricing works. #ny-svc-pricing-tldr-body = speakable. (H2: How TechBrot New York pricing works.) -#}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-svc-pricing-tldr">
  <div class="ct read read--doc">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">In one paragraph</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:16px;">How TechBrot New York pricing works.</h2>
